Mysql(sql,oracle,postgres)

Mongo > no sql
> fast 
> can save huge amount of data


Mysql > table

sno | Hindi |English | Computer
 1  |   80  |        |
 2  |       |   80   |
 3  |  80   |        |     80

MySql      Mongo
database   database
table      collections
row        documents

In Database we have table, in table we have row
In Database we have collections, in collections we have documents

var students =[
